{"name":"Warding Motes","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-deflect-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 6th level, you can expend your siphon motes to shield your allies. As a bonus action on your turn, you can expend one or more motes to create a protective barrier around you until the end of your next turn. This barrier has a radius of 10 ft and hit points equal to the number of motes expended times your proficiency bonus. The barrier has two effects. First, when an effect targets a point in space inside the barrier, it targets the surface of the barrier instead. Second, when a creature within the barrier would take damage from a source outside the barrier, the barrier absorbs that damage as long as it has hit points remaining. If multiple creatures would take damage from the same effect, you can split the absorption effect among those creatures as you choose.</p><p>In addition, when you cast any of your Line Infantry spells while the barrier is active, you can designate an additional ally within the warded zone to receive the benefits of that spell without further cost (including expending additional costly components). If the spell requires concentration and your concentration is broken, both instances of the spell are lost.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Quartus","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"10","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.BIya5jxg1bowjfC6"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675140234675,"modifiedTime":1675141148239,"lastModifiedBy":"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H"},"_id":"BIya5jxg1bowjfC6","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H":3}}
{"name":"Enhanced Piercing Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-black-pink.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 18th level, when you use your Piercing Spell feature, the target loses any resistance to the damage type dealt until the beginning of your next turn; if it was immune, it loses that immunity and gains resistance to that damage type until the beginning of your next turn.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ILsTWFFuEAjWkFNF"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675140678593,"modifiedTime":1675141148240,"lastModifiedBy":"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H"},"_id":"ILsTWFFuEAjWkFNF","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H":3}}
{"name":"Enhanced Spell Disruption","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/symbols/arrowhead-green.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 14th level, when you cast *counterspell* or *dispel magic* and must make a check to see if it succeeds, you do so at advantage.</p><p></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.OjdEGw1pVNe5S8pp"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675140608482,"modifiedTime":1675141148240,"lastModifiedBy":"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H"},"_id":"OjdEGw1pVNe5S8pp","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H":3}}
{"name":"Focused Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-green.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 15th level, you've chosen one spell to specialize in. Choose one of your warmage spells. When you cast that spell, it always acts as if it is one level higher in all respects except the spell slot needed to cast it. You can siphon motes from it as if it was the higher level; when you expend motes to further enhance it, it acts as if it was the higher level for calculating the cost.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.OxUY2n2RJx2Bx1PU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675139406108,"modifiedTime":1675141148236,"lastModifiedBy":"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H"},"_id":"OxUY2n2RJx2Bx1PU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H":3}}
{"name":"Lightning Dance","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-forked-large-orange.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif\">Starting at 11th level, your connection with flame has added an aspect of lighting. This has several effects:<br style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" />• When you use Lambent Strike or Shedding Sparks, you can choose to deal lightning damage instead of fire damage.<br style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" />• You are resistant to lightning damage in addition to fire damage.<br style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" />• You can use your Stunning Strike on the ranged attacks from your Shedding Sparks feature as if they were unarmed strikes.<br style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" />• You can spend 3 ki to cast lightning bolt as a 3rd level spell, using your Wisdom as a spellcasting modifier. This does not require any components and can deal either lightning or fire damage as you choose.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":120,"width":10,"units":"ft","type":"line"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"charges","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"wis","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["8d6","lightning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"wis"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":"ki"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"label":"Lightning Resistance","icon":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-forked-large-orange.webp","origin":"Item.P3VqFrhAtKZmVxZM","duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"disabled":false,"_id":"srqmJaLVFNNCQEyg","changes":[{"key":"@traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"lightning","priority":null}],"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{}}],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675047210808,"modifiedTime":1675050196255,"lastModifiedBy":"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H"},"_id":"P3VqFrhAtKZmVxZM","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H":3}}
{"name":"Piercing Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/targeting/target-strike-triple-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 3rd level, you have learned to augment your spells to overcome resistance and immunity. When you cast a warmage spell of 1st level or higher that deals damage, you can expend one siphon mote to ignore defenses such as Magic Resistance. If the target has immunity to the damage type, you can choose to instead deal damage of a type they are not immune to. When you do so, the target takes the 1/4 of the normal damage of the spell.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Warmage 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.QxyovgsOZL99Rwc7"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675138856302,"modifiedTime":1675141148234,"lastModifiedBy":"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H"},"_id":"QxyovgsOZL99Rwc7","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H":3}}
{"name":"Spell Efficiency","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/symbols/cog-glowing-green.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 7th level, you siphon one mote when you cast a warmage cantrip.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SUYPju5330VXIGii"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675139109818,"modifiedTime":1675141148235,"lastModifiedBy":"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H"},"_id":"SUYPju5330VXIGii","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H":3}}
{"name":"From the Ashes","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/ankh-gold-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif\">Starting at 6th level, you draw on an aspect of eternal renewal. When you use your Step of the Wind, you can choose to heal yourself an amount of hit points equal to two rolls of your martial arts die plus your Wisdom modifier. You can heal in this fashion a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.<br style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><br style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" />You also gain resistance to fire damage.<br style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Verdana, Arial, Tahoma, Calibri, Geneva, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":"When you use Step of the Wind"},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d(ceil((@classes.monk.levels +8)/6)*2) + @mod","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"label":"Fire Resistance","icon":"icons/svg/fire-shield.svg","origin":"Item.VZTvTp0K5VjwLONO","duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"disabled":false,"_id":"56gLHCA9F37AWpon","changes":[{"key":"@traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"fire","priority":null}],"tint":"#ff0000","transfer":true,"flags":{}}],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.4","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675046936890,"modifiedTime":1675050196248,"lastModifiedBy":"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H"},"_id":"VZTvTp0K5VjwLONO","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"dWkJQvEoVSj5iz4H":3}}
